				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player approaches a nymph courtesan and customer. The customer is flirting with her, and she is using it to her advantage. The player can ask if everything is all right. They can also interfere and get the drunk to leave, possibly thinking they're helping, but they're not. Both are standing.\r\n"
